dc_description_s: This polygon shapefile represents the major lakes within the United States at 1:5,000,000 scale. This layer is part of the 2014 ESRI Data and Maps collection for ArcGIS 10.2.U.S. Lakes (Generalized) provides a base map layer of major lakes of United States.
